<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ingolstadt</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Einigung mit Hermann Kepf und Hans Metmann, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen der ihnen zustehenden Leibgedinge, da auch andere Inhaber von Leibgdedingen der Adressaten ausgezahlt werden.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_78" id="38r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_78_r1l19">Der Stat cʒu Jngelſtat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_78_r1l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vn </del> Als vvir euch vormals etvvieofft <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> h </del> vnd <expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l21">von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>man</expan> keppfen vnd hanſen Metmans <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd irs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l22">leipgdings wegen . das ſie von euch vnd <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l23">vns dy <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> fürbraht . vvir Jr <expan>And<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>leute<ex>n</ex></expan> die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l24">auch <expan>leipgd<ex>ing</ex></expan> von euch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . doſſelb Jr leipgding auſʒriht vnd becʒalt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l25">darümb ſie fremde nẏmpt vves 
<add><ab facs="#facs_78_line_1577025860832_4187">ir </ab></add> ſie cʒeiht wıder Anderlewt / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l26">ſich doch gern mit euch eynen <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns gebeten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l27">euch das von Jren <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>verſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hyrümb <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l28"><expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darynne <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweiſen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l29">ſie mit euch darümb gütlich eynen laſſen wöllet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l30">Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc . <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_78" id="38r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Ingelstat</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir euch
                                                vormals etwieofft
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                                                  <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Keppfen und Hansen
                                                Metmans, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, und irs leipgdings
                                                wegen, das sie von euch und
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns dy
                                                  <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> fürbraht, wir ir
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>leute<ex>n</ex></expan>, die auch
                                                  <expan>leipgd<ex>ing</ex></expan> von euch
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, dosselb ir
                                                leipgding auszriht und beczalt, darümb sie fremde
                                                nympt, wes <add>ir</add> sie czeiht wider anderlewt,
                                                  <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> sie sich doch gern
                                                mit euch eynen <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>, und
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns gebeten, euch
                                                das von iren <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                                                  <expan>verschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Hyrümb
                                                  <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darynne
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten
                                                  <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweisen und sie
                                                mit euch darümb gütlich eynen lassen wöllet
                                                  <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
